transcript:
Customer: Hello
Executive: Hello
Customer: Hello
Executive: Hello, mein aawaz nahi aa rahi aapki.
Executive: Uh, ek second, abhi aa rahi hai meri aawaz?
Customer: Haan, abhi aa rahi hai na?
Executive: Ji, bataye.
Customer: Haan, haan.
Customer: Mein mujhe woh key ka key ring hota hai na key ring.
Executive: Ji.
Customer: Woh mujhe manufacturer jo karte hai na, unse aap mujhe jod sakte hai?
Executive: Uh, manufacturer jo karte hai, key ring?
Customer: Haan, key ring jo chavi ring hota hai na, gaadi mein chavi ring lagaya jata hai na ya car mein lagaya jata hai na.
Customer: Woh manufacturing jo karte hai, unse mujhe contact ho sakta hai kya?
Executive: Uh, ji bilkul mein kal ek baar office jaungi toh check kar lungi jo honge hamare yaha pe aur bahut clients mein unki aapko bata dungi profile.
Customer: Theek hai na, madam.
Executive: Uh, aur bhi kuch?
Executive: Okay, sir.
Customer: Nahi aur toh kuch karna nahi filhaal isi tarah.
Executive: Ji, ji bilkul mein aapko kal subah call karti hu sir 10 baje.
Customer: Theek, theek, theek, theek.
Executive: Okay sir, good night sir.
Customer: Okay.
Customer: Thank you.
